  "title": "Cashier (Karaoke) – Night Shift",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Locations:</strong> Downtown East (DTE) / Lucky Chinatown (LCT)<br />💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> $2,200 – $2,400 (inclusive of night shift allowance up to $400/month)<br />🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> 44 hours/week</p><ul><li><p><strong>DTE:</strong> 6:30pm – 3:30am / 4:30pm – 1:30am</p></li><li><p><strong>LCT:</strong> 5:00pm – 2:00am (PH Eve: 5:00pm – 3:00am)</p></li><li><p><em>Minimum 4 hours OT/week required</em></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Manage cashiering, POS system, closing payments</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries and simple service tasks</p></li><li><p>Ensure accuracy in billing & cash management</p></li><li><p>Support outlet operations during peak hours</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Comfortable handling cash & POS</p></li><li><p>Able to work night shifts</p></li><li><p>Good communication & service attitude</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Benefits</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Quarterly Performance Bonus</p></li><li><p>Referral Bonus</p></li><li><p>Medical & Dental Benefits</p></li><li><p>Birthday Ang Pao</p></li><li><p>Company Transport</p></li><li><p>Incremental Annual Leave (from 10 days)</p></li><li><p>Career Progression<br /></p><p>EA License No: 23C1703</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p></li></ul>",
